{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T08:53:16.358Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Checkpointing and recovery mechanisms"},{"type":"text","text":" in the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude Managed Agents Platform"},{"type":"text","text":" are the built-in infrastructure that automatically saves the agent's execution state so long-running tasks can be "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"paused, resumed, and rolled back"},{"type":"text","text":" without restarting from scratch. Instead of you building custom checkpointing logic, Managed Agents provides "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automatic checkpointing and session recovery"},{"type":"text","text":" as a core feature of the managed runtime."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Checkpointing in this context means:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Automatically saving agent execution state"},{"type":"text","text":" at regular intervals or after key milestones.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Preserving filesystem state"},{"type":"text","text":", conversation history, tool results, and pending work.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Enabling rollback"},{"type":"text","text":" to any previous checkpoint if the agent goes wrong.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Resuming cleanly after pauses"},{"type":"text","text":" without losing progress."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Recovery mechanisms include:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Built-in error recovery"},{"type":"text","text":" when a tool fails.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Automatic retry"},{"type":"text","text":" of failed operations.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Self-correction"},{"type":"text","text":" to recover and retry if a tool fails."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the infrastructure that traditionally took teams "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3–6 months"},{"type":"text","text":" to build: sandboxed execution, state management, credential handling, error recovery, context management, and checkpointing. Managed Agents eliminates that second job entirely."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For long-running agent tasks (minutes to hours), checkpointing is critical because:\n- Agents regularly make "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"multi-file changes"},{"type":"text","text":" that can't be easily undone with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"git"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Ctrl+Z"},{"type":"text","text":".\n- Without checkpoints, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"failure means restarting from scratch"},{"type":"text","text":".\n- With checkpoints, you can "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"rewind to any prior state"},{"type":"text","text":" and continue from there."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The practical necessity is that business automation requires checkpoints as a safety net. Checkpointing is \"absolutely critical if you're going to be using it for business processes\" like mass updates, because you need to audit decisions and revert when needed."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of checkpoints as "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"time-stamped snapshots"},{"type":"text","text":" of the entire agent work state:\n- Each checkpoint captures: timestamp, state data, tool results.\n- You can "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"rewind semantically"},{"type":"text","text":" by asking the agent to \"go back to checkpoint X\".\n- The agent finds the checkpoint ID related to the message and rewinds to that point."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Recovery is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automatic retry and self-correction"},{"type":"text","text":" layer that handles tool failures without you writing custom orchestration. If a tool fails, the platform recovers and retries by default."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How it works (Managed Agents implementation)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Automatic checkpointing"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"In Managed Agents, checkpointing is "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automatic"},{"type":"text","text":" and built into the platform:\n- The platform "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automatically saves agent execution state"},{"type":"text","text":".\n- Long-running tasks can be "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"paused and resumed at any point without restarting"},{"type":"text","text":".\n- Checkpoints are stored server-side with session state."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You don't write checkpoint code manually; you configure the agent and the platform handles it."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Recovery mechanisms"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The platform provides:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Built-in error recovery"},{"type":"text","text":" when a tool fails.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Automatic retry"},{"type":"text","text":" logic for failed operations.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Self-correction"},{"type":"text","text":" to recover and retry if a tool fails."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This means if a tool call fails (e.g., network error, API rate limit), the agent automatically retries rather than crashing."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Session state persistence"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sessions are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"stateful by design"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- They run for minutes or hours with multiple tool calls.\n- They resume cleanly after pauses.\n- They store conversation history, sandbox state, and outputs server-side."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This server-side persistence is the foundation for checkpointing. When you pause or interrupt a session, the state is preserved."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Comparison: Manual vs. Managed checkpointing"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Manual (Claude Agent SDK) pattern"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If you're building your own agent runtime, the pattern is:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Step 2: Periodic Checkpoint Saving\nimport time\ncheckpoints = []\n\ndef save_checkpoint(state_data):\n    checkpoint = {\n        \"timestamp\": time.time(),\n        \"state\": state_data,\n        \"tool_results\": response.content\n    }\n    checkpoints.append(checkpoint)\n    return len(checkpoints) - 1\n\n# Create checkpoint every hour\ncheckpoint_id = save_checkpoint({\n    \"completed_tasks\": [\"database_schema_design\"],\n    \"current_task\": \"domain_acquisition\",\n    \"pending_tasks\": [\"soc2_documentation\"]\n})"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Rollback processing pattern"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"def rollback_to_checkpoint(checkpoint_id):\n    if checkpoint_id >= len(checkpoints):\n        raise ValueError(\"Invalid checkpoint ID\")\n    target = checkpoints[checkpoint_id]\n    \n    # Restore state\n    return client.messages.create(\n        model=\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250930\",\n        max_tokens=4096,\n        tools=[{\"type\": \"memory\", \"name\": \"task_state\"}],\n        messages=[{\n            \"role\": \"user\",\n            \"content\": f\"Resume from checkpoint: {target['state']}\"\n        }]\n    )\n    \n    # Rollback on failure detection\n    if detect_failure(response):\n        response = rollback_to_checkpoint(checkpoint_id - 1)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key details:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Checkpoint frequency"},{"type":"text","text":": save at task completion OR 2-hour intervals, whichever comes first.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Performance"},{"type":"text","text":": +Checkpoints (2hr intervals) gives 89% completion rate, 4 min avg recovery time.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Semantic rewinding"},{"type":"text","text":": you can ask the agent semantically to go back to a checkpoint."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Managed Agents (no manual code)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"With Managed Agents:\n- You define the agent and tasks.\n- The platform "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automatically handles checkpointing"},{"type":"text","text":".\n- You don't write checkpoint code.\n- Recovery is "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"built-in"},{"type":"text","text":": automatic retry and self-correction on tool failures."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Checkpointing use cases"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Business automation:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Mass product updates (e.g., applying discounts to 100+ products).\n- Database migrations.\n- Code refactoring across many files.\n- Multi-step compliance audits."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Long-running tasks:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- 30-hour autonomous operations.\n- Multi-day research projects.\n- Complex data pipelines."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Development workflows:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Multi-file code changes where "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"git"},{"type":"text","text":" commits are too granular.\n- Agent-assisted refactoring where you need to audit and revert decisions."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Recovery strategies"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Built-in platform recovery"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Managed Agents provides:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Automatic retry"},{"type":"text","text":" when a tool fails.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Self-correction"},{"type":"text","text":" to recover from failures.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Built-in error recovery"},{"type":"text","text":" without custom orchestration."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Manual recovery patterns (for reference)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If you're building your own runtime, recovery strategies include:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Predictive checkpointing"},{"type":"text","text":": dynamically adjust save frequency based on task complexity (high complexity → 30-min intervals).\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"UUID-based task IDs"},{"type":"text","text":": add UUIDs to prevent duplicate execution after checkpoint restore.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Health check tools"},{"type":"text","text":": detect external dependency failures.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Exponential backoff"},{"type":"text","text":": handle API rate limit interrupts."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Performance metrics"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From actual 30-hour tasks:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion Rate"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Avg Recovery Time"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cost Efficiency"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Memory tools only"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"68%"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"-"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0x"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"+ Checkpoints (2hr)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"89%"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"4 min"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1.3x"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"+ Context editing"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"94%"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2 min"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1.1x"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Checkpoints prioritize "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"recovery speed"},{"type":"text","text":" (higher cost), while context editing reduces tokens (lower cost)."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Common failure modes"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Even with checkpointing, you need to handle:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Failure"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cause"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mitigation"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Context loss after 10 hours"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Context overflow, memory not saved"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Force memory write every 5 hours"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Duplicate execution after restore"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"State detection error"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Add UUID to task IDs, verify completion flags"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API rate limit interrupts"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Continuous requests hit ceiling"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Exponential backoff + pre-check rate limits"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"External API errors"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Undetected external dependency failures"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Add health check tools, retry logic"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"These are the failure modes you'd see when building custom checkpointing; Managed Agents handles many of these automatically."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"With Managed Agents:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- No custom checkpointing code needed.\n- Automatic checkpointing and session recovery.\n- Built-in error recovery and retry.\n- Sessions pause and resume cleanly with state intact.\n- Full session tracing in Claude Console for visibility."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Without automatic checkpointing:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- You build custom checkpointing (3–6 months of work).\n- Failure means restarting from scratch.\n- Manual error recovery and retry logic."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trade-offs"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Automatic checkpointing removes the need for custom state management.\n- Recovery is built-in, reducing orchestration complexity.\n- Sessions persist server-side with full event history."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Trade-offs:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Sessions persist data server-side, so you lose Zero Data Retention and HIPAA BAA eligibility.\n- You rely on the platform's checkpointing strategy rather than customizing it.\n- Checkpoints increase token usage compared to memory tools only."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Managed Agents provides "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automatic checkpointing and session recovery"},{"type":"text","text":" as a core feature—you don't write checkpoint code manually."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Checkpoints save the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"entire work state"},{"type":"text","text":" (filesystem, conversation history, tool results) so you can "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"rollback to any point"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Built-in error recovery"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"self-correction"},{"type":"text","text":" automatically retry failed tool calls without custom orchestration."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sessions are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"stateful by design"},{"type":"text","text":": they pause and resume cleanly with state preserved server-side."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This infrastructure traditionally took teams "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3–6 months"},{"type":"text","text":" to build; Managed Agents eliminates that work."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}}
